Oaktree Capital Management Lp decreased Vimpelcom Ltd (VIP) stake by 5.16% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Oaktree Capital Management Lp sold 252,455 shares as Vimpelcom Ltd (VIP)’s stock 0.00%. The Oaktree Capital Management Lp holds 4.64M shares with $17.87 million value, down from 4.90M last quarter. Vimpelcom Ltd now has $7.08 billion valuation. The stock rose 1.00% or $0.04 reaching $4.05. About 711,753 shares traded. VEON Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:VIP) has 0.00% since July 25, 2016 and is . It has underperformed by 16.70% the S&P500.
